description:
As Gabe, players will have to strategize quickly, as he is responsible to infiltrate, recon and execute decisively. Once inserted, Logan is his own authority -- making life and death decisions, quickly choosing his course of action. An immersive single-player experience, Syphon Filter: Dark Mirror features melee attacks, target lock, precision aiming, target and vision enhancements, enhanced artificial intelligence (AI), and high-tech weaponry. 


System Requirements:

Core 2 duo 2.4GHz or higher. (Quad Core Recommended)
nVidia GeForce GT 640 / ATI Radeon HD 6 series or higher.
3 Gig of ram or more.
OS: Windows XP / Vista / 7 / 8.1 (x86/x64)



